          "speaker": "",
          "speaker_gender": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "esES",
      "text": "«En comparación con esta herejía, todo lo que he hecho ha sido una broma».",
      "modification_date": "2023-12-01T15:03:56.8902580Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2023-12-01T15:03:56.8902588Z",
      "original_text": "\"Compared to this heresy, my work is child's play.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2023-09-12T08:36:02.4097481Z",
          "locale_text": "«¡Es más hereje que yo!».",
          "speaker": "",
          "speaker_gender": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“和你的异端恶行相比，我的所作所为简直是小打小闹。”",
      "modification_date": "2023-12-01T15:03:57.4325830Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2023-12-01T15:03:57.4325832Z",
      "original_text": "\"Compared to this heresy, my work is child's play.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2023-09-20T12:03:40.6753013Z",
          "locale_text": "“你比我更像异端分子！”",
          "speaker": "",
          "speaker_gender": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "deDE",
      "text": "\"Verglichen mit dieser Ketzerei ist meine Arbeit ein Kinderspiel.\"",
      "modification_date": "2023-12-01T17:19:17.4673002Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2023-12-01T17:19:17.4673004Z",
      "original_text": "\"Compared to this heresy, my work is child's play.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2023-10-17T09:17:03.6615713Z",
          "locale_text": "\"Ihr seid ein noch größerer Ketzer als ich!\"",
          "speaker": "",
          "speaker_gender": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "jaJP",
      "text": "「こんな異端に比べれば、{mf|俺|私}のやった事などかわいいものだ」",
